{"id":24,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":24,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".title","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f1"},[".credit",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"Mandy’s first day in her new school"]],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f2"},["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"Class, this is Mandy Cooper. Her family just moved into town, and she will be in our class. Mandy, tell us about yourself."],["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"I wish I didn’t have to do this."]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f3"},["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"Well, I’m 11 years old. And I have a little brother named Matt. He’s nine and a half. Umm …"]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f4"},["div",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"Tell us about your hobbies. What do you like to do?"]],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f5"},["div",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"I love animals, especially horses. I collect pictures and figures of horses. Someday I want to have my own horse. I like to make cookies and play soccer. Oh, and I’ve been taking piano lessons for four years, but now we have to find a new piano teacher."]],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f6"},["div",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"What else?"]],["div",{"id":"f7","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f7"},["div",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"What’s your favorite food? Do you have a favorite book?"],["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"My favorite food is my mom’s cheesy potatoes. And my favorite book is, umm … the Book of Mormon."]],["div",{"id":"f8","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f8"},["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p12"},"What’s that?"]],["div",{"id":"f9","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f9"},["div",{"id":"p13","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p13"},"What did I just say?"]],["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/friend/2013/05/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p14"},"To be continued …"]]],"refs":null}
